STR_PARAM_FARM_DESTINATION_FOOD_PROCESSING_PLANT                :Lebensmittelfabrik
STR_PARAM_FARM_DESTINATION_FACTORY                              :Fabrik

STR_PARAM_FRUIT_CHAIN                                           :Früchte-Kette
